  "detailed_description": "<h1>Discord Community</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>As the Apocalypse looms, a boy and his sheep navigate disaster together. <i>Diaspora</i> is a side-scrolling story adventure inspired by the Seven Seals of Revelation, told through a child’s perspective. The pair must use their wits to survive harsh deserts, burning farmland, and angry hordes. As they explore these haunting landscapes, the question remains: What does one seek in a world about to end?<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >KEY FEATURES</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1821970/extras/ef14863cedf48342902bd82dc3682019.poster.avif?t=1703116030\" width=650 height=366 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1821970/extras/ef14863cedf48342902bd82dc3682019.webm?t=1703116030\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1821970/extras/ef14863cedf48342902bd82dc3682019.mp4?t=1703116030\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Take control of both characters to solve puzzles and face menacing Bosses.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1821970/extras/ff0ee451f8b09af304a41792392d7a6c.poster.avif?t=1703116030\" width=650 height=366 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1821970/extras/ff0ee451f8b09af304a41792392d7a6c.webm?t=1703116030\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1821970/extras/ff0ee451f8b09af304a41792392d7a6c.mp4?t=1703116030\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Unlock a rich story inspired by the Seven Seals of Revelation.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1821970/extras/e5ff60e51f16aa569c6e9e9c8a05213b.poster.avif?t=1703116030\" width=650 height=366 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1821970/extras/e5ff60e51f16aa569c6e9e9c8a05213b.webm?t=1703116030\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1821970/extras/e5ff60e51f16aa569c6e9e9c8a05213b.mp4?t=1703116030\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Explore four distinct puzzle stages that embody different Disasters:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Unpack meaning from Desert murals<br></li><li>Navigate traps and hallucinations in Deception <br></li><li>Avoid fiery hordes in Death<br></li><li>More stages to come after Early Access!</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1821970/extras/2261d93a8c77a40c79665c0545cc2369.poster.avif?t=1703116030\" width=650 height=366 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1821970/extras/2261d93a8c77a40c79665c0545cc2369.webm?t=1703116030\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1821970/extras/2261d93a8c77a40c79665c0545cc2369.mp4?t=1703116030\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Explore a stunningly beautiful 3D world.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1821970/extras/e32f2a2fd9a06be7621e861e6920e805.poster.avif?t=1703116030\" width=650 height=366 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1821970/extras/e32f2a2fd9a06be7621e861e6920e805.webm?t=1703116030\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1821970/extras/e32f2a2fd9a06be7621e861e6920e805.mp4?t=1703116030\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Surrender yourself to <i>Diaspora</i>’s epic soundtrack.",
